		<h3><em>VideoDrums</em></h3>
		<h4>Musical Video Sequencing</h4>
		<h4><a title="Sound Art Showcase 2010: Alan Koda" href="http://facultypages.scad.edu/~aruschko/SoundArtWebsite/Alan%20Koda.html/">SCAD Sound Art Showcase 2010</a></h4>
		<%= image_tag("Videodrums1_500.png", alt: "Videodrums Screenshot 1") %>
		<%= image_tag("Videodrums2_500.png", alt: "Videodrums Screenshot 2") %>
		<p>Uses an 808-style step sequencer to drive the playhead of a video; the video (and its audio) is 'played' like a sequenced instrument.  Keyboard shortcuts allow the user multiple options during play for DJ-style live manipulation.  Markers can also be placed on the fly for instant recall of any point in the video.</p>
